<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Sports)</fld> <def>A fraudulent contest with a
predetermined winner.</def> <mark>[Slang, U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hippodrome</ent>⟦br⟧

